## Space Deva

p:The Space Deva handles calling the adventure fules from the remote servers.

### Methods

cmd:#adv hash
p:Build a hash while going along the adventure. Integrates wit the core Deva Hash feature.

#### world
cmd:#adv world:thegame 0251/main:look
p:Call a world template from an adventure server.

format:#adv world:*adventure* *id*/*template*:*part*

#### object
cmd:#adv object:thegame 0092/main:look
p:Call an object template from an adventure server.

format:#adv object:*adventure* *id*/*template*:*part*

#### agent
cmd:#adv agent:thegame 0005/main:look
p:Call an agent template from an adventure server.

format:#adv agent:*adventure* *id*/*template*:*part*

#### uid
p:Generate a uid from the Space Deva.
cmd:#adv uid

#### status
p:View the status of the Space Deva since coming online.
cmd:#adv status

#color = var(--color-orange)
#bgcolor = var(--color-black)
